### User Story

As a user, I want to scan QR code so that I can add a new contact.
* Instabug: https://dashboard.instabug.com/applications/status-10bb8cbc-15f6-44f0-8c7a-db478dc34d7d/beta/bugs/292

### Description

[comment]: # (Feature or Bug? i.e Type: Bug)
*Type*: Bug

[comment]: # (Describe the feature you would like, or briefly summarise the bug and what you did, what you expected to happen, and what actually happens. Sections below)
*Summary*: QR code scan doesn't work, camera has broken on the second address scan, and phone camera application doesn't open anymore

#### Expected behavior
[comment]: # (Describe what you expected to happen.)
QR code is shown
#### Actual behavior
[comment]: # (Describe what actually happened.)
camera has broken on the second address scan, and phone camera application doesn't open anymore

[comment]: # (Describe how we can replicate the bug step by step.)

- Open Status
- Add new contact
- Scan QR code
